{"title":"烽火台","authors":["易莎"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":1,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"烽火台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易莎用千万担土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拌和着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万滴血汗筑成的无数座烽火台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸向内地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一字儿摆开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几千年来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里曾经举起过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几亿次烽火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那血红的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇恨的火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把多少母亲的眼泪烧干……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于到了今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们的劳动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是为了战争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是为了和平在烽火台上举起的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那血红的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛过烽火的光焰的是建设者的红旗——从北京伸来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条钢铁的臂膀把几十个兄弟民族的拳头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和命运紧握在一起母亲呵当你看见这一带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再升起烟火时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请不要惊慌那浓烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是火车在喘气那亮闪闪的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是工人们在焊接钢梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}